      "text": "凄いね、こんなに人が集まってる……",
      "startTime": 2.6666667144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ステージの前も！　上も！",
      "startTime": 5.7384498194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さすがにいつもの現場とは雰囲気が違うな……\n超大御所演歌歌手の人が、すぐそこに……",
      "startTime": 12.4999999842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-13.m4a",
      "text": "リハとは全然熱気も違うね……大舞台だよ、どうする？",
      "startTime": 16.7333333176,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "どうするも何も……俺は信じて送り出すだけだ",
      "startTime": 22.2333314103,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-06.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ～！？　一緒に大舞台に立つんでしょ！？",
      "startTime": 26.7999980769,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-04.m4a",
      "text": "緊張しないの！？",
      "startTime": 29.8821174267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、舞台に立つのは麻奈だけだから\n……でも、うーん、そうだな。一緒にか……",
      "startTime": 35.4333371324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_hey-01.m4a",
      "text": "大舞台を前に、今どんなお気持ちですか？",
      "startTime": 40.8333371324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-06.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ、{user}くん、答えて！",
      "startTime": 44.514216275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "私もインタビュアー、やってみたかったんだよねー",
      "startTime": 47.4333317918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだな。これまで一緒に頑張ってきた分は\n麻奈がステージに連れて行ってくれる",
      "startTime": 55.4666646166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それが分かっているので、なんの不安もありません",
      "startTime": 58.2999979499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……{user}くん……",
      "startTime": 62.1333312832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-05.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよね。今日まで一緒に積み重ねてきたもんね",
      "startTime": 64.7043154969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、その\n頑張ったのはもちろん麻奈だからな",
      "startTime": 71.2333206021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも、頑張れたのは",
      "startTime": 74.0333206021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-01.m4a",
