      "text": "今年最後の元気を、みんなに贈ります！",
      "startTime": 104.5954110023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（大舞台でも、あいつは変わらないな）\n（……こちらこそ、いつもありがとう、麻奈）",
      "startTime": 112.700010157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
